    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>South Korea is experiencing the community transmission of the SARS-CoV-2 Omicron variant (B.1.1.529). We estimated that the mean (\u00b1 standard deviation) serial interval was 2.22 (\u00b1 1.62) days, and the basic reproduction number was 1.90 (95% Credible Interval, 1.50\u20132.43) for the Omicron variant outbreak in South Korea.</jats:p>",
